{"tid":448790,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS] 喪屍多人連線合作射擊遊戲 - Zevolution","createTime":"2017-10-26T13:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T12:52:05.000Z","uid":9699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8056889e41f5867654228fa114ba5ba4bacf37fd","tid":448790,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"見隻驚新出，但好少香港玩家玩，所以開post睇下有無人玩<br />\n<br />\nAppStore搵Zevolution或者進化啟示錄就搵到<br />\n<br />\n玩法：最多有3隻角色比你揀，但開頭得一隻就係渣機關槍既大隻佬，遊戲有分主線故事，多人合作模式（通關第一章之後先可以同人連線，一場可以有4個玩家合作打喪屍），官方遲d會出pvp玩家對戰同團戰模式，不過pvp要等下啦<br />\n<br />\n另外可以抽武器，唔課金打一排夠1000武器券就可以抽，10抽必出必出一把紫武（武器強度：橙&gt;紫&gt;藍&gt;綠&gt;一般），或者你課金買把紫武都得，月卡28蚊港幣，每日100鑽，一把武器都係1000-2000鑽<br />\n<br />\n可以開公會，但等多人玩先算，現階段籌夠多d香港人玩<br />\n<br />\n遊戲截圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/195956_691130ebeecb9e7ef77fe1a656c15835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F195956_691130ebeecb9e7ef77fe1a656c15835.jpg&h=ac90b602&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/195957_972f8c6fe20a4583991f63cf48f6fa6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F195957_972f8c6fe20a4583991f63cf48f6fa6e.jpg&h=03a5485c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下載link: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1278796885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fid1278796885&d=laFKm61w4pFflOus5mMtkC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3a4c6c68\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1278796885</a>"},{"pid":"6d8d75444876dfb7fdc4dc1fa441a819b0de4f97","tid":448790,"uid":9699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"{ISH"},{"pid":"b6577bf7d1b0245ad5f45e90e044390bf1cee7f6","tid":448790,"uid":127193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"睇落幾有趣，依家dl黎睇下<img